      z-index: 5;
      opacity: 0.65;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
    }
&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;embed video-player&#34;&gt;
    &lt;iframe class=&#34;youtube-player&#34; type=&#34;text/html&#34;
        width=731 height=410
        src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ef-hb9FmGUo?rel=0&#34;
        allowfullscreen frameborder=&#34;0&#34;&gt;
    &lt;/iframe&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;youtube-caption&#34;&gt;
        Defiance
    &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We received the task to create an emergent game in a group. The result is a blend of platforming and challenging puzzles set in a procedurally generated labyrinth that&amp;rsquo;s deeply rooted in Greek mythology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The labyrinth houses many dangers and secrets, from traps and enemies, to hidden items and potions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At the end of it three Greek goddesses await you to test your wits and give you a different reward depending on how you choose to deal with the situation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;roles--responsibilities&#34;&gt;Roles &amp;amp; Responsibilities&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;game-design&#34;&gt;Game Design&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Concept for an endless runner/platformer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Controls (Keyboard/Mouse &amp;amp; Gamepad)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;level-design&#34;&gt;Level Design&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extended procedural level generator&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Level editor to enable designers to create levels using our existing structures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;code&#34;&gt;Code&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Player character&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;UI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extended procedural level generator&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interactions, movement abilities &amp;amp; special weapons&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sounds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;art&#34;&gt;Art&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Normal maps (WIP)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;VFX: Trail particles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
